{"word":"G5011 - ταπεινός - tapeinós - tap-i-nos' - Base","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ταπεινός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">tapeinós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">tap-i-nos'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Base</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தாழ்ந்த, சிறுமை, தாழ்மையான, தாழ்மையுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"low"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Of uncertain derivation; <i>depressed</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>humiliated</i> (in circumstances or disposition): - base, cast down, humble, of low degree (estate), lowly.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5011/5011\">G5011</a>, <a href=\"#/G5012/5012\">G5012</a>, <a href=\"#/G5013/5013\">G5013</a>, <a href=\"#/G5014/5014\">G5014</a>"}]}